SELECT DISTINCT "catalogue_product"."id", "catalogue_product"."structure", "catalogue_product"."is_public", "catalogue_product"."upc", "catalogue_product"."parent_id", "catalogue_product"."title", "catalogue_product"."slug", "catalogue_product"."description", "catalogue_product"."meta_title", "catalogue_product"."meta_description", "catalogue_product"."product_class_id", "catalogue_product"."rating", "catalogue_product"."date_created", "catalogue_product"."date_updated", "catalogue_product"."is_discountable", EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_option" U0 INNER JOIN "catalogue_productclass_options" U1 ON (U0."id" = U1."option_id") WHERE U1."productclass_id" = ("catalogue_product"."product_class_id") LIMIT 1) AS "has_product_class_options", EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_option" U0 INNER JOIN "catalogue_product_product_options" U1 ON (U0."id" = U1."option_id") WHERE U1."product_id" = ("catalogue_product"."id") LIMIT 1) AS "has_product_options", "catalogue_productclass"."id", "catalogue_productclass"."name", "catalogue_productclass"."slug", "catalogue_productclass"."requires_shipping", "catalogue_productclass"."track_stock" FROM "catalogue_product" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalogue_productclass" ON ("catalogue_product"."product_class_id" = "catalogue_productclass"."id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalogue_product" T4 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T4."parent_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_stockrecord" ON (T4."id" = "partner_stockrecord"."product_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_partner" ON ("partner_stockrecord"."partner_id" = "partner_partner"."id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_partner_users" ON ("partner_partner"."id" = "partner_partner_users"."partner_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_stockrecord" T9 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T9."product_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_partner" T10 ON (T9."partner_id" = T10."id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "partner_partner_users" T11 ON (T10."id" = T11."partner_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalogue_product" T13 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T13."parent_id") WHERE ("catalogue_product"."parent_id" IS NULL AND ("partner_partner_users"."user_id" IS NULL OR T11."user_id" IS NULL) AND (UPPER("catalogue_product"."title"::text) LIKE UPPER('%Shared%') OR UPPER(T13."title"::text) LIKE UPPER('%Shared%'))) ORDER BY "catalogue_product"."date_created" DESC
